==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[abscisus]]'', past participle of ''[[abscidere]]'', formed from ''[[abs-]]'' + ''[[caedere]]'' "to cut".

===Pronunciation===
* ''[[RP]]:''
** {{IPA|/əbˈsaɪz/}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|abscis|ing}}

